chris schiller (b. january 18, 1977 in rochester, new york) is a lacrosse player for the rochester knighthawks in the national lacrosse league. in 2006, he was named the team's unsung hero. schiller also plays for the toronto nationals of major league lacrosse (mll). schiller works as an endoscopic account specialist for johnson & johnson. he majored in marketing at penn state university and is married to his wife jennifer.